CLass Loader Subsystem

Loading

It will create an object of type  Class
Note:
Class is predefined class/object in java

Any runtime info about the class we can getv it through Class Object

package com.ashokit.demo.strings;

;

public class Test {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		Test test = new Test();
		
		Class cls= test.getClass();
		System.out.println(cls.getName());
		System.out.println(cls.getSuperclass());
		

	}
}


